{"tid":1452652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[無底線奪權運動]五大訴求就係阻礙運動既大台","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:45.000Z","uid":265750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63fb86f00b6d4d75353a1b2c9c749ad69f50d307","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:56:52.000Z","msg":"五個訴求只係將權力送俾政府主宰運動方向。<br />\n就算五個訴求俾你實現哂、有雙普選啦<br />\n仲有警隊幫親中人士助選，實行軍政府治港<br />\n你收貨咩?<br />\n其實整場運動本質一開始就係對政府不信任，<br />\n大家都心知肚明呢個政府唔推翻，5個訴求根本無從落實。<br />\n<br />\n香港人對政府仲係有太多幻想，仲停留係要政府&quot;回應訴求&quot;做goal<br />\n而政府一早就已經<strong>拒絕</strong>左五大訴求。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係拒絕左啦!醒下啦香港人!</span></span></strong><br />\n無論我地有幾激烈既行動都好<br />\n如果都只回歸返訴求，都只係賦予政府權力繼續打壓。<br />\n政府冇當過我地係香港人，<br />\n政府冇當過我地係人，<br />\n政府當我地係異己者，用盡一切方法消滅；<br />\n而我地仲一廂情願覺得政府會聆聽聲音!?<br />\n5大訴求已經承托唔到成場運動<br />\n唔通(如果)捉哂柒婆一哥係手仲問佢回唔回應訴求?<br />\n五大訴求就係阻礙運動既大台<br />\n規條左我地運動既模式<br />\n而香港已經進入左無險可守既攬炒階段，仲想和平示威簡直痴心妄想。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong>香港人點解要訴要求，仲要用乞求姿態要人俾你<br />\n爭氣少少，準備好執政意志<br />\n記住主權在民</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人要行動</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要奪權</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要話事</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲有一點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">速戰速決</span><br />\n事實係我地冇勢冇錢冇人(相對上)<br />\n有既只係爆炸力<br />\n拖延黎打只會令更多人向利益歸邊、俾對家慢慢收籠。<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔需要懷憂喪志，<br />\n勇敢打一場仗。<br />\n當咁多人連命都唔要走上前線為香港，<br />\n同樣地我地都應該要有信心可以奮身再為香港打拼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2360004bacb2e82302eb6d983b4d7a201ab32898","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:09:51.000Z","msg":"希望香港人記係心<br />\n自己先係權力中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bf84ad8c6fa5b2f3b98747e1aacbfdae059625","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b821453b1618200261877fba6977133d46a0081b","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bec653098912b17697083c9f2c2ac51b83343e","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d499c614ef03b40524c5ce45f4b20e8a68e3bc4","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4710fb6c4035bd5dbdbf32304d9dce3dd8c29f","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a884c7dadf649e89e3bf667466332292937b523","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02a8b39361768fd4361d1a7c5cee8ad05b78536","tid":1452652,"uid":265750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"可唔可以多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}